sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_078_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Invalid CentralSystemCertificate Security Event
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports Security profile 2 and/or 3

    CS->>CP: 1. InstallCertificate.req
    Note right of CS: certificateType = CentralSystemRootCertificate<br/>certificate = <Configured certificate>

    CP-->>CS: 2. InstallCertificate.conf
    Note left of CP: status = Rejected
    Note over CP: OCTT rejects any certificate for this test

    CP->>CS: 3. SecurityEventNotification.req
    Note left of CP: type = InvalidCentralSystemCertificate

    CS-->>CP: 4. SecurityEventNotification.conf
